Swiss public transport API

Swiss public transport API

tapi(.endpoint, ..., .protocol = "https", .version = "v1")

Arguments

.endpoint

path to api endpoint - there are three endpoints available: locations, connections, and stationboard.
...

named parameters will be translated into a request query. For the full documentation see https://transport.opendata.ch/docs.html
.protocol

protocol to be used
.version

api version

Value

list of dataframes
